desc: A Dallas located home fragrance company, established in 2020.

layout.text:
Delicate Wicks is a Texas based home fragrance company owned and operated by Marina London.
She believes that fragrance is an extension of your home design and aims to create high quality products with accessible price points in mind.
The products offered are all made in small batches, ensuring the best quality and fragrances possible.
All products used are appropriately sourced, and eco – friendly.
Please stay engaged – and keep an eye out for new products and blends. Xo.
